div.p: This architecture diagram illustrates a mini data platform where synthetic sales data is generated and stored in MinIO, orchestrated and cleaned through Apache Airflow, persisted in Postgres, and finally visualized in Metabase. The flow includes branching, retries, and fallback mechanisms to ensure reliable, auditable data ingestion.
